  <brief_title>Glulisine + Lantus in Type I Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>26-week, International Multicenter, Open, Non-randomized Phase III Clinical Trial for Evaluation of Efficacy and Safety of Insulin Glulisine (HMR1964) Injected Subcutaneously in Subjects With Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus Also Using Insulin Glargine</official_title>
