  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy (in terms of change HbA1c from baseline to endpoint) and safety (in
      terms of adverse events, clinical chemistry, lipids, hematology) of insulin glulisine (HMR
      1964) in subjects with type I diabetes mellitus
    </textblock>
